NAAN MUDHALVAN

Naan Mudhalvan is a flagship initiative launched by the Government of Tamil Nadu to enhance the skills of students across the state. The program aims to equip students with industry-relevant skills, career guidance, and training opportunities to improve their employability.

The initiative focuses on:

Skill development programs

Career counseling and guidance

Competitive exam preparation

Industry-oriented training

Personality development

Internship and placement support

Naan Mudhalvan provides access to various courses in emerging technologies such as Artificial Intelligence, Data Science, Cyber Security, Cloud Computing, and other high-demand fields. The platform connects students with industry experts and training partners to ensure quality learning.

The main objective of Naan Mudhalvan is to empower students to become confident, skilled, and job-ready professionals who can contribute effectively to society and the economy.
